OL,3,CGlass panels completely removed after
OL,4,Cvandals target seafront
OL,6,FThe remaining glass panels at South
OL,7,FShield's amphitheatre have been
OL,8,Fremoved due to ongoing vandalism.
OL,10,FSouth Tyneside Council said they
OL,11,Fregretfully had to make the decision
OL,12,Fin the light of "continued antisocial
OL,13,Fbehaviour and targeted damage".
OL,15,FWindows were smashed at the
OL,16,Famphitheatre on the promenade on
OL,17,FSandhaven Beach on consecutive Fridays
OL,18,F- 19 January and 26 January.
