OL,6,FEarlier this week, the council
OL,7,Fconfirmed patrols had been stepped up
OL,8,Fto try and deal with the issue.
OL,10,FIn a statement on Friday 2 February,
OL,11,Fthe authority said: "As a result of
OL,12,Fcontinued anti-social behaviour and
OL,13,Ftargeted damage we regret to say that
OL,14,Fthe decision has been taken to remove
OL,15,Fthe remaining glass panel windows from
OL,16,Fthe walkway.
